###Window###
>>> after installing monogdb 
>>> in C: drive create folder by name of data/db

> c:\program file\mongodb\3.4\bin

open 2 cmd with above location

in first cmd > mongod   (this will start mongo server)
in second cmd> mongo    (this will start mongo console)


###Mac###
>open terminal>  mongod   (this will start mongo server)
>open terminal>  mongo    (this will start mongo console)

port 27017

